for more than four months, suffered heavy casualties but giving
no figures.
</P>
<P>
ECOMOG, toppling the military regime of Major Johnny Paul
Koroma in Freetown and restoring President Ahmed Tejan Kabbah to
power in March, has been since engaged in mopping-up operations.
