<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index up 3.0 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, August 15 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange index
closed at 2,090.5 Saturday, up 3.0 points from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 113.03 million shares changed hands in 1,843 deals
as against 85.19 million shares in 1,767 deals Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The turnover rose to 15.69 million Kuwaiti dinars (51.77
million U.S. dollars) from Wednesday's 14.97 million dinars (49.40
million dollars). 
</P>
