</P>
<P>
-- With another two tonnes of medicine arriving in Nairobi
Friday, Egypt has delivered a total of five tonnes of
pharmaceuticals after the devastating bomb attack on the
U.S. embassy there.
</P>
<P>
On Friday, two bomb explosions occurred near the U.S. embassies
in Kenya and Tanzania minutes apart, in which over 200 people have
been confirmed killed and more 4,000 others injured.
</P>
<P>
