Argentina, Brazil, Chile and the United States, to reach a final
agreement was fundamental.
</P>
<P>
Conflict between Lima and Quito flared up in the past week,
when Peru claimed that 300 Ecuadoran soldiers had entered a
disputed area, and were holding 18 square kilometers of Peruvian
territory. 
