<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, August 14 (Xinhua) -- Argentine Mariano Puerta became
the lone unseeded player in the last four of the 300,000 U.S.
dollars San Marino tennis tournament by beating his compatriot on
Friday.
</P>
<P>
