that the OAU ministerial committee dealing with the crisis has
affirmed that the Badme Area was under Ethiopian administration
prior to the period between May 6 and 12, 1998.
</P>
<P>
The statement said, ''In the face of incontrovertible evidence,
the OAU committee conclusively affirmed that Badme Area has been
administered by Ethiopia''. (Ethiopia-Ethio-Eritrean Crisis)
